| Change <Obey$Dir>.Fortunes to be the name of the fortunes file to be used.
| If it is in the Fortunes directory, prefix the name with <Obey$Dir>. as
| in the line below.

Set Welcome$FortuneFile <Obey$Dir>.Fortunes

| Change 4 to be the number of lines (ie. the number of fortunes) contained
| in the file (or the number of fortunes to be used, if less).

SetEval Welcome$Fortunes 4

RMEnsure Fortune 0.00 RMLoad <Obey$Dir>.Fortune